1139
00:43:55,719 --> 00:43:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] da se oslobodiš tiranina.

1140
00:43:59,440 --> 00:44:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ko su onda najveći tiranini u našem životu?

1141
00:44:01,760 --> 00:44:04,840
