1146
00:44:18,860 --> 00:44:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo kojeg.

1147
00:44:19,699 --> 00:44:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Društvenog, osobnog.

1148
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] Emocionalnog.

1149
00:44:23,159 --> 00:44:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] Emocionalnog.

1150
00:44:24,039 --> 00:44:25,920
