1158
00:44:46,820 --> 00:44:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ljudi ne mogu povezati i ratove i ljubav.

1159
00:44:49,619 --> 00:44:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] A ljubav je snaga potrebna da se sukobiš, da se oslobodiš tiranina.

1160
00:44:57,260 --> 00:45:00,079
