1181
00:45:51,300 --> 00:45:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što sam ja znao raditi i što je radilo puno ljudi koje sam vidio oko sebe.

1182
00:45:56,159 --> 00:45:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] Počela manipulirati sa svojom traumom.

1183
00:45:58,639 --> 00:45:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam jadan.

1184
00:45:59,800 --> 00:46:00,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ucijenjivati.

1185
00:46:00,739 --> 00:46:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ucijenjivati.

1186
00:46:02,239 --> 00:46:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] manipulacija.

1187
