1210
00:46:34,760 --> 00:46:37,280
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, od onda ste puno mudri, je li tako?

1211
00:46:37,280 --> 00:46:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto sam mudri.

1212
00:46:38,039 --> 00:46:38,719
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto mudri.

1213
00:46:38,719 --> 00:46:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ste već sad spomenuli djevojku koja vas je,

1214
00:46:42,539 --> 00:46:45,260
[SPEAKER_01] kako sam rekla, otpilila, dakle ostavila zbog toga,

1215
00:46:45,260 --> 00:46:47,639
[SPEAKER_01] ali jako puno danas ljudi ucijenjuju.

1216
00:46:47,639 --> 00:46:50,820
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne znam, evo, u svakodnevnom životu, znaš,

1217
00:46:50,880 --> 00:46:54,699
