1219
00:46:56,940 --> 00:47:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ne mogu biti koncentrirani ili koncentrirana na poslu,

1220
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] jer imam bolesnu majku, zahtjevno dijete,

1221
00:47:02,119 --> 00:47:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] ljubomornog muža ili suprugu.

1222
00:47:04,340 --> 00:47:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav je granica.

1223
