1224
00:47:10,880 --> 00:47:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] ne petljati se.

1225
00:47:11,659 --> 00:47:13,800
[SPEAKER_00] I da znam sad je dosta.

1226
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] Nosi se.

1227
00:47:15,159 --> 00:47:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može.

1228
00:47:16,579 --> 00:47:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ne dolazi u obzir.

1229
00:47:17,760 --> 00:47:20,320
[SPEAKER_00] Pod bilo kojim uvjetima to se neće desiti.

1230
00:47:20,880 --> 00:47:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bez uvjeta, bez uvjeta.

1231
00:47:22,380 --> 00:47:25,900
