1236
00:47:34,400 --> 00:47:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ni meni nije uvijek odgovarala.

1237
00:47:36,139 --> 00:47:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sam ja bio, dan nisam vrijedan,

1238
00:47:38,900 --> 00:47:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] sam mislio, pa sam imao strah od neuspjeha,

1239
00:47:40,900 --> 00:47:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam imao strah od propuštanja,

1240
00:47:42,539 --> 00:47:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam bio ohol, pa sam bio bahad,

1241
00:47:44,980 --> 00:47:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam, meni se sve te istine nisu svidjela.

1242
00:47:47,619 --> 00:47:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to su bile nužne istine koje su mi donale do osobne slobode.

1243
