1251
00:48:05,300 --> 00:48:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' zvuči logično?

1252
00:48:07,199 --> 00:48:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] Moram vam reći, inače, cijeli svimri je užasno logičan.

1253
00:48:09,860 --> 00:48:12,860
