[SPEAKER_00] Putin. Putin i Trump.

1287
00:49:19,420 --> 00:49:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] Susjeda, žena.

1288
00:49:21,699 --> 00:49:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] Muž.

1289
00:49:22,539 --> 00:49:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] Muž je dobar.

1290
00:49:24,079 --> 00:49:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] Posao.

1291
00:49:24,820 --> 00:49:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] U, posao.

1292
00:49:25,900 --> 00:49:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] Šef je grozan, a šefica...

1293
00:49:28,500 --> 00:49:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] Brozni su.

1294
00:49:29,059 --> 00:49:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] Da su oni bolji, ja bi bio bolji.

1295
00:49:31,320 --> 00:49:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno.

1296
00:49:31,900 --> 00:49:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] Sve smo riješili.

1297
00:49:33,800 --> 00:49:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] Sve smo riješili.

1298
00:49:34,440 --> 00:49:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] Mi samo bacamo odgovornost van sebe.

1299
00:49:37,380 --> 00:49:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] Država je odgovorna za moju sreću.

1300
00:49:41,900 --> 00:49:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nemoj maliti.

1301
00:49:43,219 --> 00:49:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, čekat ćemo grad, državu.

1302
00:49:46,099 --> 00:49:47,760
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj, nije to na nama.

1303
00:49:48,059 --> 00:49:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, kažem, nije na nama.

1304
00:49:48,940 --> 00:49:49,679
[SPEAKER_00] Čija je zgrada?

1305
00:49:49,679 --> 00:49:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, dobro, naša, ali mislim, grad treba to riješiti.

1306
00:49:53,300 --> 00:49:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] Grad treba riješiti.

1307
00:49:54,900 --> 00:49:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, kažem, sram vas budi sve.

1308
00:49:56,440 --> 00:50:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, kad to kažeš, pa je, mislim, naša je zgrada.

1309
00:50:01,820 --> 00:50:03,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je, naša je zgrada.

1310
00:50:03,380 --> 00:50:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] Onda nemojte odbacivati odgovornost, nego idemo dignuti kredit.

1311
00:50:06,099 --> 00:50:09,960
